<text id="A7108T">
<front id="d2">
<div1 type="summary" id="d3">
<p>Standard request for schoolbooks (largely arithmetic textbooks).</p> 
</div1> 
 
</front> 

<body id="d4">
<div1 type="letter" id="d5">
<head>
<name type="recipient">Mr Whiting</name> 
<name type="place">Staunton Va</name> 
</head>

<opener>
<dateline>
    <date value="1866-01-12">Jan 12/66</date> 
</dateline> 
<salute></salute> 
</opener> 

<p>In case you have not already sent 50 copies of Greenleafs Arith, or Thompsons Arith (Com. School) or Practical) you will please send 50 copies of (Greenleafs Com. Schl Arith or the same no of Thompsons Practical also 40 <del hand="h1">35</del> " Colton &amp;Fitches Introductory Geography
</p>

<closer>
<salute></salute> 
<signed>John Scott</signed> 
<seg type="postscript">P. S. If you find that (from the 1<hi rend="super">st</hi> to the 8<hi rend="super">th</hi>) you sent the <del hand="h1">book</del> 50 copies of Arith.  Then forward me immediately <hi rend="underline">by Express</hi> 40 copies of Colton &amp;Fitches Geog. (Introductory) and <hi rend="underline">I</hi> will pay the Expressage </seg> 
 
</closer> 
</div1> 
</body> 
</text> 
